 điểu phú - 鵩鳥賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-Ngh%E1%BB%8B/author-P4_Isc8PaPS-90054lCyPA">Giả Nghị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/Quan-%C4%91%E1%BA%A5u-k%C3%AA-ng%E1%BA%ABu-t%C3%A1c/poem-WIgJ1H1dslHxSYm8YVunow">Quan đấu kê ngẫu tác - 觀鬥雞偶作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%C3%A1i-vi%C3%AAn/poem-7af6N1m7ClDjE32KuEDMJg">Thái viên - 菜園</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/Tr%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-U9ThM86uHnVwR_2o75TB5Q">Trách tử - 責子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
